Package: tidymatrix
Title: Tidyverse-Style Operations on Matrices with Row and Column Metadata
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Raivo", "Kolde", , "rkolde@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a unified data structure for matrices with associated row
    and column metadata, enabling tidyverse-style data manipulation. Inspired by
    tidygraph's approach, users can activate rows, columns, or the matrix itself
    to perform operations using familiar dplyr verbs while maintaining
    consistency across all components.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Imports: 
    dplyr,
    magrittr
